   "source": [
    "# Matrix Calculus \n",
    "\n",
    "Jacobian, gradient is transpose of Jacobian.  \n",
    "\n",
    "Some common derivatives ($A$ a matrix, $x$ a vector): \n",
    "1. $D_x Ax = A$\n",
    "2. $D_x x^TA = A$\n",
    "3. $D_xx^TAx = x^T(A + A^T)$\n",
    "4. $D_x x^Tx = 2x^T$. \n",
    "\n"
   ]
  }
